### 

@base_url = http://localhost:5000


### POST Sign Up test1

POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/signup HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test1@gmail.com",
  "fullName": "test1",
  "password": "12345678",
  "username": "test1"
}


